                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable R</hi> 114.) I took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined.</hi> Did he appear to be sober? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, quite.</p>
